314
00:16:56,300 --> 00:16:59,730
Hayate!!!

315
00:17:12,350 --> 00:17:14,950
Did you call for me, Milady?

316
00:17:17,130 --> 00:17:19,870
Hayate, why are you here?

317
00:17:19,870 --> 00:17:21,580
Why?

318
00:17:21,580 --> 00:17:23,920
Because you called for me.

319
00:17:27,550 --> 00:17:31,500
I have not forgotten the pain you've caused me.

320
00:17:30,650 --> 00:17:33,660
Is there anywhere that hurts, Milady?

321
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:35,430
I will now return all that back to you.

322
00:17:33,660 --> 00:17:35,430
No, I'm fine.

323
00:17:35,430 --> 00:17:37,760
I see. That's good to hear.

324
00:17:35,430 --> 00:17:37,760
Hey, stop ignoring me!

325
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:43,110
You don't need to rush; I will have you
take responsibility for endangering Milady.

326
00:17:43,390 --> 00:17:46,350
Could he possibly be angry?

327
00:17:46,350 --> 00:17:49,600
And when those who usually don't get angry get angry...

328
